<denchmark-h:h1>KEY:TYPE=VALUE</denchmark-h>

<denchmark-h:h1>KEY is the name of a variable in the cache.</denchmark-h>

<denchmark-h:h1>TYPE is a hint to GUIs for the type of VALUE, DO NOT EDIT TYPE!.</denchmark-h>

<denchmark-h:h1>VALUE is the current value for the KEY.</denchmark-h>

